I am very disappointed with the quality of the food and the punctuality of the delivery. The rice, chicken, plantains, were dry and tasteless. The entire order costed $44 and some odd cents and I didn't enjoy any of it. And to make matters worse, the restaurant was extremely late in making/delivering my order. I will not be ordering again from them. I strongly advise against patronizing this establishment!  EDIT: After a few hours of eating this food, I became very sick. Stomach pain, nausea, and severe heart burn. Please do not order from this restaurant.. I think I have food poisoning, because my stomach was hurting really bad. Partially because the food was half DONE!
